Text.Text:
1. Each ranger draws 1 path card

2. Rangers take turns in any order, on turn either: 
-Perform a test
-Play a card

3. Decide whether to travel

4. Draw 1 ranger card, reset energy pools, ready all cards

1. Commit effort:
-Commit 1 or more energy of a matching aspect
-Commit approach icons by discarding cards from hand
-Commit effort from other sources

2. Draw challenge card and apply modifier

3. Resolve challenge effects
